  "name": "Holy Avenger Longsword",
  "type": "weapon",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<div class=\"item-attunement\"><i>(Requires attunement by a Paladin)</i></div><p>You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. When you hit a &amp;Reference[fiend]{fiend} or an &amp;Reference[undead]{undead} with it, that creature takes an extra 2d10 &amp;Reference[radiant]{radiant} damage.</p>\n<p>While you hold the drawn sword, it creates an aura in a 10-foot radius around you. You and all creatures friendly to you in the aura have advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects. If you have 17 or more levels in the paladin class, the radius of the aura increases to 30 feet.</p>\n</div>",
